This paper is about query performance prediction (QPP), which is a subfield of information retrieval (IR). Therefore, cs.IR is the most likely category. The paper also discusses machine learning models and feature selection, which are common topics in the subfields of machine learning (cs.LG), natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and databases (cs.DB).
